"different from the ones for 2–4 \\faPeopleGroup! \\textbf{Some cards have a "
"text saying} \"5–10 \\faPeopleGroup\": the rules here are for games from 5 "
"to 10 players. For games with 2–4 \\faPeopleGroup, go to page "
